QuestData.Title: Crate of Crab Meat
QuestData.Description: This crate, labeled 'Crab Meat', seems to have fallen from a recently sunken cargo ship.$b$bAdarrah would surely welcome such a find, considering the ordeal she's had to endure.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Crate of Crab Meat to Adarrah in Smuggler's Scar.
QuestData.RewardText: Why, $n! What a surprise!$b$bIf anyone ever calls your character into question you be sure to send them my way.$b$bI'll tell anyone who'll listen that in my moment of need, you gave me a case of crabs...
